{
  "text": ", where a, b > 1, will not appear in the OPE to the first subleading order and so we leave their discussion to future work. Mellin transform of graviton scattering amplitudes in string theory [CITATION_1] is well defined without the time coordinate u. In this case the correlation function with the insertion of a holomorphic supertranslation descendant is given by a simple change of (4.7),",
